## 🔍 Duplicate Detection System

**This node's function:**
- Detects previously sent news
- Prevents sending the same news multiple times
- Uses global static data for persistent memory

**Code explanation:**
```javascript
// Create global data storage
const staticData = this.getWorkflowStaticData('global');
staticData.sentLinks = staticData.sentLinks || [];

// Filter out previously sent items
items = items.filter(item => {
  if (staticData.sentLinks.includes(item.json.link)) {
    return false; // Already sent
  }
  staticData.sentLinks.push(item.json.link);
  return true; // New news
});
```

**Key features:**
- Persistent data storage
- Automatic duplicate prevention
- Memory cleanup (optional)
